			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>Join us and Transform Health.</strong></p>
<p>
Transform Health is a young, venture-backed startup that works at the intersection of technology, design, and healthcare. We are transforming how people care for themselves and their families through elegant mobile software and unique mobile hardware products. These products also advance our overall mission: to create the world&rsquo;s first real-time map of human health.</p>
<p>
Our company&rsquo;s first product is a simple, ultra-low-cost <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="smartphone:0" grmarkguid="c8ef462b-0f26-45c2-b692-bae53f2dc131" gruiphraseguid="ea64a56f-b420-4114-b8ec-8e917a80a8aa">smartphone</span>-connected thermometer. Parents can easily capture their child&#39;s temperature, seek advice from a medical professional, compare symptoms to &quot;what&#39;s going around&quot; in the local area, and keep records of health issues. These connected devices &ndash; along with others &ndash; also help us create tools such as the <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="health:0" grmarkguid="273f4587-4075-4166-bb39-9b8844e88482" gruiphraseguid="3fc19064-90bc-4bb3-b1b0-cb464054a170">health</span> map, empowering local parents, physicians, and educators with information to help track and stop the spread of disease.</p>
<p>
Our founders and executives have collectively started several successful ventures, invented next-generation technologies, and led programs that have put millions of people onto life-saving treatment. We have a bold mission, a plan to achieve it, and the funding to make it happen. Join us.</p>
<p>
<strong>Who are we looking for?</strong></p>
<p>
We are looking for an outstanding software engineer to help us forever change the way people view their health. Our technology stack will include several of the following: Ruby on Rails, Hadoop, Post-GIS, Kafka, and Storm. We take a parallel and <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="real-time approach:0" grmarkguid="a69595f6-6394-45fe-b796-74c906c07fc4" gruiphraseguid="3f0d8b10-eeb6-4ce8-83bb-a60d0812e2a2">real-time approach</span> to analytics and data science.</p>
<p>
As an early employee and <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="core member:0" grmarkguid="f3913ab1-2dfe-4ad0-8166-75e46b2c781d" gruiphraseguid="7a00f4aa-0d17-495a-87be-f88fc73c3d03">core member</span> of our software team, you will play a significant role in the development of a unique product and platform.</p>
<p>
<strong>You should be interested in:</strong></p>
<p>
&bull; Using your skills to have a widespread impact on people (we are a mission-first company)<br />
&bull; Rolling up your sleeves to tackle big technical challenges with a hypothesis-driven approach</p>
<p>
<strong>You will develop <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="our:0" grmarkguid="deeb1683-eb7b-4dfc-ad8a-973608dbb293" gruiphraseguid="fc5006e0-c7c7-4a37-9aee-897584bdffb4">our</span>:</strong></p>
<p>
&bull; Back-end &ldquo;health GIS&rdquo; platform that aggregates real-time data from partners &ndash; health and non-health data including real-time data feeds from major social media and location based companies &ndash; to derive insights on the spread of illness and wellness<br />
&bull; Mobile software apps, which interact with various <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="smartphone:0" grmarkguid="7e8d4a00-3dad-49ea-8ad9-f7ff679c7a5d" gruiphraseguid="b9ad92d9-93cf-486c-84fa-fe278b3b6edf">smartphone</span>-connected medical hardware devices</p>
<p>
<strong>You should:</strong></p>
<p>
&bull; Be a great hacker and a brilliant coder, familiar with low level programming languages<br />
&bull; Have a CS degree from a top tier school (masters degree preferred)<br />
&bull; Have a record of exceeding expectations with <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="minimum:0" grmarkguid="2fc9d909-64f9-4cb0-aa99-ee0fa1e4f79a" gruiphraseguid="e88b0297-3e82-43c0-81d3-0001b4f6b952">minimum</span> of 2-3 years industry experience<br />
&bull; Be active in the local software community (e.g., <span class="GRnoSuggestion GRcorrect" grcontextid="hackathons:0" grmarkguid="25ed269e-a3e2-4be8-919a-6c32f1898dfb" gruiphraseguid="2c76969b-5a44-4906-a5a4-e43706e694f5">hackathons</span>, <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="meetups:1" grmarkguid="a403e14e-1497-47d2-b6df-93bf20bfaf4d" gruiphraseguid="2c76969b-5a44-4906-a5a4-e43706e694f5">meetups</span>, <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="etc:2" grmarkguid="630cd524-e328-426c-b9ed-9b942bd22e45" gruiphraseguid="2c76969b-5a44-4906-a5a4-e43706e694f5">etc</span>)<br />
&bull; Be willing to relocate to either SF or NY</p>
<p>
Please contact Inder Singh, our founder and CEO, directly: inder@transformhealth.me</p>
