&bull; Knowledgeable (or willing to rapidly learn from our team) about the software-hardware integration challenges of connecting a device to a <span class="GRcorrect" grcontextid="smartphone:0" grmarkguid="4aef96c7-52e0-4d7b-bc50-71d37a2209fd" gruiphraseguid="75e392b6-9c82-4dec-aa3c-c6584e237812">smartphone</span><br />
